longBusinessSummary: Heliostar Metals Ltd. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in North America. The company explores for gold and silver deposits. It primarily holds a 100% interest in the Unga Gold project that covers an area of 250 square kilometers located in Alaska, the United States. The company was formerly known as Redstar Gold Corp. and changed its name to Heliostar Metals Ltd. in October 2020. Heliostar Metals Ltd. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
